The paper presents a novel algorithm for constructing and initializing deep neural networks based on decision trees, which is a topic closely related to machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The proposed algorithm is applied to a variety of regression and classification datasets, which suggests that the paper may also belong to computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the efficiency and computational cost of the proposed algorithm, which may indicate that it could also be relevant to data mining (cs.DM) sub-category.
